data.description: Welcome to your dream home on the corner lot! This charming abode, perfect for first-time homeowners, boasts a modern open concept design, flooded with natural light and featuring updated fixtures throughout. Tile flooring spanning throughout the main living areas. Built just five years ago, this home comes with the assurance of a foundation warranty, providing peace of mind for years to come. Powered by efficient natural gas and equipped with a tankless water heater with endless hot water.  Outside, the rock landscaping and contemporary oversized paver walkway welcome you home. Step onto the newly stained deck in the backyard, complete with a cozy fire pit area, perfect for gatherings under the stars. A spacious metal shed offers ample storage, while the expansive backyard leaves plenty of room for your imagination to roam.  Located conveniently near highways 1604 and 90, this home offers easy access to all the amenities of city life without the burden of city taxes. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this corner lot sanctuary yours!
